data.description: Indulge in luxury living in this stylish 2-bed, 2-bath with den, nestled in a sought-after retirement community, with a stunning backdrop overlooking the picturesque 11th hole. Enjoy the openness of the Helena floor plan, well-equipped kitchen, and serene outdoor space. Easy access to community amenities and golfing facilities. Both AC and water heater have been recently replaced. Garage wired with a 220v.
